710747f-a.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 30th Street
710747f-a.text:
12th Avenue, east side, from W. 30th (right) to 33rd (left)
Streets, showing the New York Central Railroad yards. In the centsr
are the sheds that lie between 31st and 32nd Streets. The 2-story
hay lofts on the left are on the north side of 33rd Street. In the
background is the outstanding Empire State Building.
April 22, 1931
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
NO EEPRODUCTIOS
